data.basic-usage#Basic Usage:
Just do three steps:
Tag your HTML with data-murphy:
<div data-murphy="left-to-right">Any content here</div>
Reset your CSS:
*[data-murphy] {
  opacity: 0;
}
Start MurphyJS:
import murphy from "murphyjs-lib";
murphy.play()
That's it! ü§üüèø

data.2-reset-your-css#2. Reset your CSS:
In your CSS, reset all the tagged elements:
*[data-murphy] {
  opacity: 0;
}
